Name: Jubilee
About the game: Jubilee is about pure precision platforming . Jump and spin through a variety of challenges: no upgrades, no power-ups. Collect gems and rescue animals. There's multiple routes through the diverse regions of the world: make your own way to the exit... and freedom! They locked you up for not paying your debt. Who put them in charge anyway!? You were never gonna pay in the first place...
